                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="r-footer">
                    <div style="font-weight: 800; color: #000; margin-bottom: 5px;">ARCZEN DIGITAL ASSETS | AG_SYSTEM_RECEIPT_V2</div>
